  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We hypothesize that when compared to usual care a greater proportion of hospitalized diabetic
      patients who are candidates for cholesterol lowering will be discharged with a prescription
      for a statin if their physicians are contacted by a pharmacist to discuss treatment
      guidelines.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
